rows.label: tlk43310141_03_msg0001
rows.name:
The Superbians came at us without
even the slightest warning. That's
pretty low, even for them.

rows.label: tlk43310141_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Half of the Divine Beast
battleships and their crews
won't make it back from Temperantia.

rows.label: tlk43310141_03_msg0003
rows.name:
Ah, it's a shame it came to this.
It's probably too late even to get
out of the way of the war now.

rows.label: tlk43310141_03_msg0004
rows.name:
Those Superbians are going to find
out the hard way the costs of messing
with us, you can count on that.
